response.original_title: Set Your Champion Free: Claiming Your Birthright
response.overview: “Set Your Champion Free” features motivational author, coach, and speaker Lisa Nichols as she offers a transformational message, affirming the unlimited potential of your inner champion. As this short film pulses with life, allow it to awaken your inner self-esteem and inspire you to be your best in becoming part of the world’s solutions, rather than its problems.
response.tagline: Featuring the spoken wisdom of motivational speaker, Lisa Nichols, this WisdomFilm catalyzes the unlimited potential of our inner champion and invites us to remember our greatness.
response.title: Set Your Champion Free: Claiming Your Birthright
